name: PoS-32
additional_notices: Kindly be aware of liquidity-related risks. This notice is not directed at any project in particular, and is more of a cautionary reminder.

The following token has a variable tax function on the smart contract to change tax rates post deployment.
Do your own research and be careful if you are trading this token.

description.en: The merge is here! PoS-32 is a community-focused protocol allowing holders to seamlessly earn by participating in validating on the Ethereum Network by simply staking their $POS32 token. No need for ETH, no need for any technical know-how. PoS-32 Protocol handles all the complexities of staking, operating a validator node and rewards distribution. You simply stake and earn.
